19 November Minister of Justice and Correctional Services, Ronald Lamola will today brief media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on Wednesday, 18 November 2020. The details of the briefing are as follows:Date:  Thursday, 19 November 2020Time: 13h00Venue: GCIS – Ronnie Mamoepa Press Room, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria. NB: There will be a video link to Imbizo Media Centre in Parliament. Media Participation: Journalists may view the briefing via live streaming on the South African Government social media channels on the links below:Facebook: http://facebook.com/GovernmentZATwitter: http://twitter.com/GovernmentZAYouTube: http://youtube.com/GovernmentZA Enquiries:Phumla WilliamsCabinet SpokespersonCell: 083 5010 139